{"tid":1544897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍到發黑]分享下如何比深藍更深藍","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:24:46.000Z","uid":916,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1924562aee0661e462880745d09b916c7dd94d","tid":1544897,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"我講緊果啲唔係其他po可以感化到果啲藍<br />\n而係冇人性, 不分善惡, 唔講logic果種, 仲要將佢地嘅歪理周圍同人講<br />\neg: 要出解放軍殺哂啲黑衫, 死百幾人好小事<br />\n唯一方法就係比佢地更痴線令佢地收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntopic 1: 戒嚴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 要戒嚴啦, 睇班黑衫仲敢唔敢出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係囉係囉, 應該叫哂啲解放軍落黎, 每30米就企一個, 一見到人就查身分證, 如果係30歲以下果D一律塔番上新彊果D再教育營, 冇357年都唔好放番出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 仲有呀, 如果發現有30歲以上包庇佢地啲仔女, 做父母嘅都要一齊塔上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:..............<br />\n<br />\ntopic 2: 831太子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: D暴徒係地鐵搞事, 仲係度嘈話唔見左幾個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實駛咩咁麻煩呀, 下次地鐵有事, 叫啲速龍拎機關槍入車廂見人就射, 全部咸魚唔郁得咪唔會唔岩數<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 場面咁緊急, 啲差人唔會有時間分清楚邊啲係暴徒架啦, 我覺得全部射死哂就最安全。因為冇一個係無辜架, 佢出現左係車廂就係佢抵死, 死幾百人好小事姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:..............<br />\n<br />\ntopic 3: 學生罷課<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (都係果啲廢話)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我覺得果啲攪事學生應該全部捉番去佢地學校入面, 當住其他學生面將佢地槍斃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 佢地啲父母都應該要槍斃, 教左個咁唔愛國嘅細路出黎同叛國冇分別<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:..............<br />\n<br />\n大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60bb8d3d1d22833d1d58bd0c03d3815047e8efd","tid":1544897,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b279cfd5d214336b81d25cbc26407ce820e3ed22","tid":1544897,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba79fea51a3ddd54c57156410d7f0c4d6a31ad21","tid":1544897,"uid":916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"有冇痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" c